                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1638-18490820 t18490820-1638-punishment-136"></join>Confined One Year</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">SMITH</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
